<h3 id="X3026">X(3026)&nbsp;=&nbsp;10th STEVANOVIC POINT</h3>
Trilinears&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; f(a,b,c)
: f(b,c,a) : f(c,a,b), where f(a,b,c) = bc(b + c - a)(b -
c)<sup>2</sup>(a<sup>2</sup> + ab + ac + 2bc)<sup>2</sup><br>
Barycentrics&nbsp;&nbsp; af(a,b,c) : bf(b,c,a) : cf(c,a,b)
<p>X(3026) lies on the incircle and these lines:
150,388&nbsp;&nbsp; 274,1682&nbsp;&nbsp; 1111,1357&nbsp;&nbsp;
